00:30:11,060 --> 00:30:12,420
Of course!

593
00:30:12,660 --> 00:30:13,540
By how much?

594
00:30:15,660 --> 00:30:16,260
How much?

595
00:30:18,860 --> 00:30:19,860
One or two points.

596
00:30:20,300 --> 00:30:21,300
One point or two points?

597
00:30:23,980 --> 00:30:24,620
One point.

598
00:30:26,340 --> 00:30:27,020
Do you know how

599
00:30:27,020 --> 00:30:28,740
many people you've put behind by one point?

600
00:30:29,100 --> 00:30:29,940
One point!

601
00:30:30,740 --> 00:30:31,380
Listen to me.

602
00:30:31,380 --> 00:30:32,500
One point in NCEE

603
00:30:32,500 --> 00:30:33,820
puts tens of thousands behind.

604
00:30:33,820 --> 00:30:34,940
And you belong with them.

605
00:30:34,940 --> 00:30:35,660
No, that's you!

606
00:30:35,660 --> 00:30:37,620
If only I transferred here two years earlier.

607
00:30:37,620 --> 00:30:39,140
Then I could help you study sooner.

608
00:30:40,620 --> 00:30:41,300
It's alright.

609
00:30:41,420 --> 00:30:42,460
The exam is behind us.

610
00:30:42,540 --> 00:30:44,500
You really didn't pay attention at first.

611
00:30:44,780 --> 00:30:46,180
When 12th grade just started,

612
00:30:46,180 --> 00:30:47,060
what were you doing?

613
00:30:47,060 --> 00:30:48,460
Fooling around every day.

614
00:30:49,260 --> 00:30:50,100
Do you regret it?

615
00:30:50,780 --> 00:30:51,400
Not funny.

616
00:30:58,140 --> 00:30:58,820
However,

617
00:30:59,660 --> 00:31:01,020
Tsinghua or Peking are the same.

618
00:31:01,780 --> 00:31:02,820
You're still alone

619
00:31:03,460 --> 00:31:04,380
and look up to the

620
00:31:04,380 --> 00:31:05,540
stars with yourself.

621
00:31:07,660 --> 00:31:08,500
That's right.

622
00:31:09,220 --> 00:31:09,900
Dude,

623
00:31:10,300 --> 00:31:11,140
don't feel alone.

624
00:31:11,460 --> 00:31:12,740
Didn't we have a deal?

625
00:31:13,100 --> 00:31:14,740
After the NCEE,

626
00:31:14,740 --> 00:31:16,860
we'd go to Chengdu and find Qin.

627
00:31:16,860 --> 00:31:17,620
Right.

628
00:31:17,740 --> 00:31:19,420
We finally saw Qin last time,

629
00:31:19,420 --> 00:31:21,460
but didn't get a great reunion because of Ma Tian.

630
00:31:21,820 --> 00:31:22,420
Right.

631
00:31:23,340 --> 00:31:24,700
We're all going this time.

632
00:31:24,700 --> 00:31:25,900
It will be fun!

633
00:31:27,380 --> 00:31:27,980
Oh right,

634
00:31:28,300 --> 00:31:29,180
how was your NCEE?

635
00:31:30,700 --> 00:31:32,460
What do you expect?

636
00:31:32,940 --> 00:31:34,300
That kind of thing happened before NCEE.

637
00:31:34,300 --> 00:31:35,380
And I couldn't find you anywhere.

638
00:31:35,820 --> 00:31:37,380
Do you think I'm in the mood to take it?

639
00:31:39,700 --> 00:31:41,140
We can study for another year.

640
00:31:42,940 --> 00:31:44,620
More study?

641
00:31:48,220 --> 00:31:49,940
Let's study hard for another year.

642
00:31:50,940 --> 00:31:51,560
Then,

643
00:31:51,980 --> 00:31:54,180
we'll get into the same university.

644
00:31:56,700 --> 00:31:58,100
Come to think of it,

645
00:31:58,100 --> 00:31:59,460
that's awesome.

646
00:32:26,180 --> 00:32:26,780
Liangliang.

647
00:32:27,900 --> 00:32:28,540
What's up?

648
00:32:29,980 --> 00:32:30,660
Dad,

649
00:32:32,340 --> 00:32:33,460
am I useless?

650
00:32:35,260 --> 00:32:36,820
Nonsense!

651
00:32:40,580 --> 00:32:42,420
You got so many things for me,

652
00:32:42,420 --> 00:32:43,860
are you worried that

653
00:32:44,020 --> 00:32:45,100
I won't survive?

654
00:32:46,340 --> 00:32:46,940
Of course not.

655
00:32:48,980 --> 00:32:51,660
My friends already got admission letters from the second batch.

656
00:32:51,660 --> 00:32:52,860
I still have nothing.

657
00:32:53,940 --> 00:32:55,300
Then wait a little longer.

658
00:32:56,300 --> 00:32:58,540
What if there's no letter for me?

659
00:33:00,300 --> 00:33:01,260
You've been saving up,

660
00:33:02,340 --> 00:33:03,580
and you have so many plans.

661
00:33:06,060 --> 00:33:07,740
I feel I'm really sorry to you.

662
00:33:08,860 --> 00:33:10,020
I owe you so much.

663
00:33:10,300 --> 00:33:11,940
Stop talking about that.

664
00:33:14,180 --> 00:33:14,820
Liangliang,

665
00:33:15,780 --> 00:33:17,100
I just saw this in the mailbox

666
00:33:17,100 --> 00:33:18,060
downstairs.

667
00:33:18,060 --> 00:33:18,980
Open it yourself.

668
00:33:27,500 --> 00:33:31,100
I'm admitted!

669
00:33:34,220 --> 00:33:35,540
You're a college student!

670
00:33:35,540 --> 00:33:36,860
Don't break your back.

671
00:33:36,860 --> 00:33:37,820
Behave yourself.

672
00:33:38,140 --> 00:33:39,420
Liangliang is a college student.

673
00:33:46,620 --> 00:33:47,660
Time for lunch.

674
00:33:48,780 --> 00:33:50,180
I'll get you something to eat.

675
00:34:00,900 --> 00:34:03,020
Didn't you already have your admission letter?

676
00:34:03,740 --> 00:34:04,660
Why are you still down?

677
00:34:05,500 --> 00:34:06,460
Yeah, Teaty.

678
00:34:07,300 --> 00:34:08,420
You all got yours.

679
00:34:08,420 --> 00:34:09,540
I'm the only one left.

680
00:34:09,540 --> 00:34:10,740
And you're still down.

681
00:34:10,820 --> 00:34:11,900
What do you want?

682
00:34:11,900 --> 00:34:12,660
Right.

683
00:34:16,780 --> 00:34:18,300
Mom, dad.

684
00:34:18,740 --> 00:34:20,100
Can I not go to college?

685
00:34:22,220 --> 00:34:23,860
If I go to college,

686
00:34:24,420 --> 00:34:26,060
I can only come back once a week.

687
00:34:26,500 --> 00:34:27,380
Who's there for you?

688
00:34:27,380 --> 00:34:28,380
You're getting old.

689
00:34:28,380 --> 00:34:29,500
It's inconvenient

690
00:34:29,500 --> 00:34:30,620
for you to move around.

691
00:34:30,620 --> 00:34:32,180
I'm really not going to college.

692
00:34:33,100 --> 00:34:33,700
Liangliang,

693
00:34:34,740 --> 00:34:35,700
give me a second.

694
00:34:36,260 --> 00:34:37,860
I'm really not going to college.

695
00:34:41,140 --> 00:34:41,740
Liangliang.

696
00:34:43,700 --> 00:34:44,820
See this?

697
00:34:45,660 --> 00:34:47,220
I can't see.

698
00:34:47,220 --> 00:34:49,500
I can't see clearly, dad.

699
00:34:51,620 --> 00:34:53,780
These are plane tickets for your mom and me.

700
00:34:54,340 --> 00:34:55,420
What tickets?

701
00:34:56,140 --> 00:34:57,980
Your mom and I have decided.

702
00:34:59,060 --> 00:35:00,460
When you're off to college,

703
00:35:01,140 --> 00:35:03,219
we'll stop worrying and go travel

704
00:35:04,340 --> 00:35:06,020
to places we like.

705
00:35:07,620 --> 00:35:08,739
Think about it.

706
00:35:10,100 --> 00:35:11,980
If you don't go to college,

707
00:35:12,219 --> 00:35:14,259
How can we go travel

708
00:35:14,259 --> 00:35:15,980
in a good mood?

709
00:35:16,500 --> 00:35:18,179
You have plans to travel!

710
00:35:19,340 --> 00:35:21,460
Can you save me the worry?

711
00:35:22,659 --> 00:35:25,219
Don't worry, Liangliang.

712
00:35:26,580 --> 00:35:29,659
Take care of yourselves.

713
00:35:30,140 --> 00:35:32,300
Don't go to crowded places.

714
00:35:32,500 --> 00:35:34,420
Don't walk too far on a hike.

715
00:35:35,699 --> 00:35:36,940
Don't save up anymore.

716
00:35:36,940 --> 00:35:39,260
Spend money on good food, clothes and hotels.

717
00:35:39,500 --> 00:35:41,780
Don't just think about saving everything for me.

718
00:35:41,780 --> 00:35:43,140
I have no use for them.

719
00:35:43,180 --> 00:35:45,180
I'm a grown-up now.

720
00:35:46,980 --> 00:35:47,740
Liangliang,

721
00:35:48,940 --> 00:35:50,260
you've grown up.

722
00:35:51,300 --> 00:35:52,620
You're a man.

723
00:35:53,100 --> 00:35:53,860
I am.

724
00:35:54,500 --> 00:35:56,460
A man should never drop tears easily.

725
00:35:57,220 --> 00:35:58,460
I won't.

726
00:35:58,460 --> 00:36:00,140
I won't.

727
00:36:22,900 --> 00:36:23,740
What's up?

728
00:36:24,100 --> 00:36:25,300
I'll help you, Qin.

729
00:36:26,900 --> 00:36:28,260
You have brains like a poached egg.

730
00:36:28,700 --> 00:36:29,580
Can you count?

731
00:36:31,780 --> 00:36:32,820
A poached egg? Really?

732
00:36:35,060 --> 00:36:36,180
Of course I can.

733
00:36:36,220 --> 00:36:37,900
I got 56 in math.

734
00:36:38,180 --> 00:36:39,260
So impressive.

735
00:36:39,260 --> 00:36:40,500
Of course,

736
00:36:40,500 --> 00:36:42,020
I only need four more for a pass.

737
00:36:44,940 --> 00:36:45,660
Where's Xin?

738
00:36:46,420 --> 00:36:47,300
Grabbing noodles.

739
00:36:52,700 --> 00:36:55,180
You're doing well with the street stall.

740
00:36:55,820 --> 00:36:56,700
Yeah.

741
00:36:56,700 --> 00:36:58,620
I paid Xin back in only a few days.

742
00:37:01,420 --> 00:37:02,500
Are you two

743
00:37:02,500 --> 00:37:03,780
never going back to Chongqing?

744
00:37:05,140 --> 00:37:06,220
He's so stubborn.

745
00:37:06,220 --> 00:37:07,540
I'll wait for him to come around.

746
00:37:08,940 --> 00:37:10,980
Girls like you are a rare kind.

747
00:37:10,980 --> 00:37:12,300
You're really faithful.

748
00:37:13,900 --> 00:37:15,460
Xin is the same.

749
00:37:17,940 --> 00:37:18,980
Right.

750
00:37:18,980 --> 00:37:21,580
Nothing was going well when I first came to Chengdu.

751
00:37:21,580 --> 00:37:24,060
It only got better after Xin came.

752
00:37:25,820 --> 00:37:27,780
When we just started,

753
00:37:27,780 --> 00:37:29,140
I was here every day,

754
00:37:29,140 --> 00:37:30,140
Xin handled pick-up runs.

755
00:37:30,940 --> 00:37:33,340
Every time, she was exhausted when she came back.

756
00:37:33,340 --> 00:37:34,740
I only knew later.

757
00:37:34,740 --> 00:37:37,380
There's still some distance between here and the bus stop.

758
00:37:37,380 --> 00:37:39,740
To save money, she never called a ride.

759
00:37:39,740 --> 00:37:41,140
She always ran back.

760
00:37:41,500 --> 00:37:42,420
Really?

761
00:37:43,580 --> 00:37:45,700
That's the relationship Xin and I have.

762
00:37:46,060 --> 00:37:47,100
Understand now?

763
00:37:53,580 --> 00:37:55,060
Is your birthday coming soon?

764
00:37:56,500 --> 00:37:57,500
How did you know?

765
00:38:08,060 --> 00:38:09,100
How did you know?

766
00:38:09,940 --> 00:38:11,180
Ma Tian told me.

767
00:38:11,180 --> 00:38:12,900
He asked me to get you a birthday cake.

768
00:38:13,740 --> 00:38:14,980
He's giving me a surprise?

769
00:38:15,620 --> 00:38:16,300
Yeah.

770
00:38:22,180 --> 00:38:24,500
Then why are you telling me now?

771
00:38:25,140 --> 00:38:27,180
You're so annoying, dummy.

772
00:38:43,420 --> 00:38:44,040
Baorong,

773
00:38:44,500 --> 00:38:45,740
go back without me tonight.

774
00:38:46,820 --> 00:38:47,420
Why?

775
00:38:48,220 --> 00:38:49,620
Need to pick up something from Qin.

776
00:38:50,780 --> 00:38:52,140
Buying me a birthday cake?

777
00:38:54,460 --> 00:38:55,260
How did you know.

778
00:38:55,940 --> 00:38:57,820
It's all because of Qin.

779
00:38:57,820 --> 00:38:59,180
Unreliable.

780
00:38:59,180 --> 00:39:00,700
He told me in advance.

781
00:39:02,900 --> 00:39:04,740
And there's no surprise.

782
00:39:07,340 --> 00:39:08,460
Are you disappointed?

783
00:39:13,100 --> 00:39:13,700
It's fine.

784
00:39:13,700 --> 00:39:15,420
I'm still happy.

785
00:39:15,420 --> 00:39:17,060
I'll just pretend I don't know anything.

786
00:39:17,620 --> 00:39:18,380
Retard.

787
00:39:19,780 --> 00:39:20,620
Oh right.

788
00:39:20,620 --> 00:39:22,060
What's your birthday wish?

789
00:39:22,060 --> 00:39:23,980
I'll make it happen for you.

790
00:39:24,980 --> 00:39:26,700
I won't tell you

791
00:39:28,060 --> 00:39:29,100
my birthday wish.

792
00:39:29,100 --> 00:39:30,420
Otherwise, it won't come true.

793
00:39:30,420 --> 00:39:31,980
Li Yaohui.

794
00:39:31,980 --> 00:39:33,300
He Baorong.

795
00:39:34,260 --> 00:39:35,220
Li Yaohui.

796
00:39:45,820 --> 00:39:46,900
Did you know,

797
00:39:48,540 --> 00:39:49,940
it's Hercules Jiao's birthday today.

798
00:39:51,540 --> 00:39:53,060
We always celebrated her birthday

799
00:39:54,020 --> 00:39:56,060
in this yard every year.

800
00:39:58,940 --> 00:40:00,060
18 years old.

801
00:40:00,780 --> 00:40:01,940
Becoming an adult.

802
00:40:07,900 --> 00:40:09,580
I wonder how she's doing today, if she's

803
00:40:11,380 --> 00:40:13,060
having a good time with Ma Tian in Chengdu.

804
00:40:15,540 --> 00:40:16,260
Why laugh?

805
00:40:17,100 --> 00:40:18,940
When I just transferred here,

806
00:40:18,940 --> 00:40:20,580
I thought you two were a couple.

807
00:40:21,140 --> 00:40:23,260
Back then, Jiaojiao liked you.

808
00:40:26,340 --> 00:40:27,620
You too.

809
00:40:27,620 --> 00:40:29,100
I thought you were with Ma Tian.

810
00:40:29,340 --> 00:40:30,340
You moved to my table.

811
00:40:30,340 --> 00:40:32,220
I thought you were helping him screw me.

812
00:40:36,540 --> 00:40:37,980
How time flies.

813
00:40:44,500 --> 00:40:46,060
I'm going to leave.

814
00:40:49,220 --> 00:40:50,300
Did you think about

815
00:40:51,460 --> 00:40:52,620
what you're going to say to me

816
00:40:53,540 --> 00:40:54,660
at the day I'm leaving?

817
00:41:06,300 --> 00:41:06,980
Honestly.

818
00:41:08,940 --> 00:41:10,140
I've thought about it.

819
00:41:13,060 --> 00:41:14,020
But I don't know yet.

820
00:41:14,900 --> 00:41:16,220
That's because you never studied.

821
00:41:21,940 --> 00:41:23,540
What do you want me to say?

822
00:41:25,420 --> 00:41:26,780
How would I know?

823
00:41:26,980 --> 00:41:28,900
Should I draft something up for you

824
00:41:29,180 --> 00:41:31,380
and ask you to read it to me when I leave?

825
00:41:34,940 --> 00:41:36,660
How about I'll tell you what I think

826
00:41:37,660 --> 00:41:39,300
after we go see Qin in Chengdu?

827
00:41:48,340 --> 00:41:48,980
Leave it.

828
00:41:48,980 --> 00:41:49,600
Liu.

829
00:41:51,100 --> 00:41:51,740
Chen,

830
00:41:53,300 --> 00:41:53,980
we're closed.

831
00:41:55,700 --> 00:41:56,420
Here's the thing.

832
00:41:57,060 --> 00:41:58,380
The other day, my son came back

833
00:41:58,860 --> 00:42:00,620
and told me you gave him some beef noodles.

834
00:42:01,260 --> 00:42:02,740
It was a great chunk of beef.

835
00:42:02,740 --> 00:42:03,820
It was delicious.

836
00:42:05,260 --> 00:42:06,300
It's fine.

837
00:42:08,140 --> 00:42:08,860
Here.

838
00:42:08,860 --> 00:42:09,660
What?

839
00:42:10,420 --> 00:42:11,300
Noodle money.

840
00:42:14,860 --> 00:42:17,380
I just won it over mahjong.

841
00:42:19,420 --> 00:42:20,020
Right.

842
00:42:20,300 --> 00:42:21,580
Chen, good luck.

843
00:42:28,860 --> 00:42:29,660
Noodle money.

844
00:42:30,420 --> 00:42:31,140
Happy now?

845
00:42:33,180 --> 00:42:33,780
Yes.

846
00:42:34,020 --> 00:42:35,500
Told you I'd get it.

847
00:42:38,660 --> 00:42:39,660
What are you doing?

848
00:42:39,660 --> 00:42:40,700
It's almost 12 o'clock.

849
00:42:40,700 --> 00:42:41,820
Where's the cake?

850
00:42:43,660 --> 00:42:44,420
I'll get it.

851
00:42:44,860 --> 00:42:46,300
Where is it?

852
00:42:46,300 --> 00:42:47,580
Hurry up, I'll wait.

853
00:43:11,420 --> 00:43:12,260
Qin.

854
00:43:12,460 --> 00:43:13,420
What is it?

855
00:43:13,420 --> 00:43:14,380
Someone took the bag.

856
00:43:15,900 --> 00:43:16,540
And the money?

857
00:43:17,260 --> 00:43:18,180
In the bag.

858
00:43:19,980 --> 00:43:21,260
Never mind, Qin.

859
00:43:21,260 --> 00:43:23,060
I promised I'd get it for you.

860
00:43:23,740 --> 00:43:24,900
Qin.

861
00:43:25,660 --> 00:43:26,500
Listen.

862
00:43:27,060 --> 00:43:28,500
If it weren't for Qin,

863
00:43:29,020 --> 00:43:30,100
would you probably not come

864
00:43:30,100 --> 00:43:31,140
to our school?

865
00:43:31,580 --> 00:43:32,300
What do you think?

866
00:43:33,420 --> 00:43:35,100
If I didn't know Qin,

867
00:43:35,100 --> 00:43:36,820
you wouldn't be my table-mate.

868
00:43:36,820 --> 00:43:37,460
Yeah.

869
00:43:37,780 --> 00:43:38,740
Then I wouldn't have

870
00:43:38,740 --> 00:43:40,300
such a good table-mate.

871
00:43:40,300 --> 00:43:41,260
Of course.

872
00:43:48,500 --> 00:43:49,700
Anything else?

873
00:43:52,860 --> 00:43:54,500
Don't you think it's a pity?

874
00:44:06,780 --> 00:44:08,500
I might have hurt him before.

875
00:44:09,300 --> 00:44:10,500
He also hurt me.

876
00:44:12,140 --> 00:44:13,380
But we had the same reason.

877
00:44:14,140 --> 00:44:16,060
It's the same kind of fondness.

878
00:44:18,140 --> 00:44:20,500
It's quite ironic, come to think of it now.

879
00:44:27,100 --> 00:44:27,900
Yeah.

880
00:44:30,820 --> 00:44:32,780
Fortunately, everyone's living a good life now.

881
00:44:37,220 --> 00:44:38,140
Thief!

882
00:44:38,820 --> 00:44:39,740
Stop!

